## 通过Swift的Visison框架抠图

```
REMOVEBG_PNGQUANT=1 ./removebg 1 ./input/pigRelax/ ./output/pigRelax/ --outputFmt png

./removebg 1 ./input/pigStudy/ ./output/pigStudy/ --outputFmt webp --webpQuality 100
```


## A2D文件操作说明

### 将webp序列打包封装到a2d文件
```
python ani2d_tool.py encode \
  --inputImgs "../swift/output/pigSleep/%03d.webp" \
  --stateNames default \
  --fps 15 \
  --sizeMode auto \
  --atlasOptimize auto \
  --aniFile output/pigSleep.a2d \
  --rawFrameFormat webp

python ani2d_tool.py encode \
  --inputImgs "../swift/output/pigWorking/%03d.webp" \
  --stateNames default \
  --fps 15 \
  --sizeMode auto \
  --atlasOptimize auto \
  --aniFile output/pigWork.a2d \
  --rawFrameFormat webp \
  --workers 8
```

python ani2d_tool.py encode \
  --inputImgs "../swift/output/pigWork/%03d.webp" \
  --stateNames default \
  --fps 15 \
  --sizeMode auto \
  --atlasOptimize auto \
  --aniFile output/pigWorking.a2d \ 
  --rawFrameFormat=webp \
  --workers=8

python ani2d_tool.py encode \
  --inputImgs "../swift/output/pigWorking/%03d.webp" \
  --stateNames default \
  --fps 15 \
  --sizeMode auto \
  --atlasOptimize auto \
  --aniFile output/pigWork.a2d \
  --rawFrameFormat webp \
--workers=4